Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.37,0:00:08.33,Default,Mega Man,0,0,0,,There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.97,0:00:13.86,Default,Mega Man,0,0,0,,I can see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.83,0:00:26.73,Default,Mega Man,0,0,0,,Rush!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.83,0:00:36.73,Default,Mega Man,0,0,0,,Rush!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.77,0:00:43.60,Default,Mega Man,0,0,0,,Rush!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.70,0:00:48.70,Default,Dr. Wily,0,0,0,,You’ve done well to\Nmake it this far, Mega Man!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.03,0:00:53.21,Default,Dr. Wily,0,0,0,,But it seems this is\Nwhere we part ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.23,0:00:58.50,Default,Dr. Wily,0,0,0,,Now watch from the afterlife\Nas I conquer the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.53,0:00:59.60,Default,Dr. Wily,0,0,0,,Farewell!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.17,0:01:23.93,Default,Mega Man,0,0,0,,Rush!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.10,0:01:25.93,Default,Mega Man,0,0,0,,Rush...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.90,0:01:29.60,Default,Duo,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.83,0:01:31.73,Default,Mega Man,0,0,0,,You’re...!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.17,0:01:34.06,Default,Duo,0,0,0,,My name is Duo.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.30,0:01:39.86,Default,Duo,0,0,0,,I was created to eliminate\Nevil energy from the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.13,0:01:49.73,Default,Duo,0,0,0,,Here it comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.46,0:02:24.43,Default,Mega Man,0,0,0,,Duo,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.46,0:02:26.20,Default,Mega Man,0,0,0,,That’s the same from last time...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.70,0:02:27.83,Default,Duo,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.86,0:02:30.83,Default,Duo,0,0,0,,In this planet’s terms,\Nit is called evil energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.10,0:02:33.90,Default,Duo,0,0,0,,What I’ve discovered up until now
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.93,0:02:38.06,Default,Duo,0,0,0,,is that those who possess this\Nenergy’s source harbor evil hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.57,0:02:42.46,Default,Duo,0,0,0,,This energy absorbs evil hearts\Nto create a physical form.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.23,0:02:46.53,Default,Duo,0,0,0,,It’s still growing stronger…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.10,0:02:51.26,Default,Duo,0,0,0,,If we don’t stop it soon, this planet\Nwill be consumed by evil energy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.57,0:02:58.33,Default,Duo,0,0,0,,I can feel the energy’s\Npresence in that tower
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.17,0:02:59.93,Default,Duo,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.57,0:03:05.53,Default,Duo,0,0,0,,There’s a barrier in our way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.97,0:03:09.00,Default,Duo,0,0,0,,I’ll look for the remaining\Nenergy and deal with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.83,0:03:12.83,Default,Duo,0,0,0,,You go find the energy\Nsource and destroy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.43,0:03:14.20,Default,Mega Man,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.03,0:03:16.13,Default,Mega Man,0,0,0,,Let’s go, Rush!
